metadata.name: High Spirits
metadata.description:
Created for ONE Sydney, a 10 day program of art, music & culture by Australia’s leading social enterprise gallery, Art Aid. 

The exhibition and event series will be held from 21 July – 31 July 2022, and will feature an epic line-up of homegrown multidisciplinary creatives.

High Spirits embodies unity, togetherness and optimism. The work depicts ribbons of all colours and sizes, sailing ever-upward in parallel and implies that we can all weather uncertainty when we stick together.

80% of the sale will be donated to Minus18, Australia's charity improving the lives of LGBTQIA+ youth.
